Run script/pingerui_server.pl to test the application.
And open your browser at http://loclahost:3000/gui/display
-------------
to run it under Apache webserver with mod_perl:

add contents of the apache_perl.conf as instructed into the
apache config file and restart apache webserver.
If your apache server is running on standard port 80 then
you will be able to see pigner UI interface at:

http://yourwebserver_hostname/gui/display

-------------

